---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

import reactCourseImg from "../assets/publications/react-guide-course.png";
import aspireCourseImg from "../assets/publications/from-aspire-to-hired-cover.png";
import techVaImg from "../assets/publications/tech-va-blueprint.png";

import PageLayout from "../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
import PageMeta from "../components/PageMeta.astro";
import PageHeader from "src/components/PageHeader.astro";
import Button from "src/components/Button.astro";
---

<PageLayout>
  <PageMeta
    title="Download and buy web development ebooks and resources | Rob Kendal, freelance developer"
    description="Download helpful web development ebooks, videos and training courses on starting to code"
    slot="meta"
  />
  <section slot="main" class="mb-20">
    <div class="prose max-w-none prose-bubblegum">
      <PageHeader>Publications</PageHeader>
      <p>
        In addition to my
        <a href="/mentorship"> mentorship programs</a>
        , I'm a published author and course creator, regularly crafting content to
        help people learn to code, land their first job, and improve their coding
        life!
      </p>
      <p>
        You can view, download and purchase my recent publications right here.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="my-14">
      <div class="">
        <a
          href="https://www.newline.co/courses/beginners-guide-to-real-world-react"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <Image src={reactCourseImg} alt="The Beginners Guide to Real-World React course cover" />
        </a>
      </div>
      <div
        class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-600 border-t-0 rounded-b-sm shadow-md p-5 md:p-10"
      >
        <h3 class="heading-2 dark:text-slate-700">
          <a
            href="https://www.newline.co/courses/beginners-guide-to-real-world-react"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            The Beginner's Guide to Real-World React
          </a>
        </h3>
        <div class="prose max-w-none prose-bubblegum dark:text-slate-700">
          <p>
            My course, The Beginner's Guide to Real-World React is available now
            and well-suited to new and aspiring developers alike.
          </p>
          <p>
            It's perfect for those new to the React library and will teach you
            solid fundamentals of React development through heaps of practical
            lessons, projects and realistic examples.
          </p>
          <p>With the course, you'll get access to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>8+ hours of video,</li>
            <li>50 lessons,</li>
            <li>loads of practical React advice,</li>
            <li>project-based learning through building real applications,</li>
            <li>
              step-by-step teaching and guidance from a seasoned React
              developer,
            </li>
            <li>...and much more</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-center">
            <Button
              href="https://www.newline.co/courses/beginners-guide-to-real-world-react"
              text="Learn more"
              variant="primary"
              external
            />
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="my-8">
      <div class="">
        <a
          href="https://gum.co/WssIGB"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <Image src={aspireCourseImg} alt="From Aspire to Hired cover" />
        </a>
      </div>
      <div
        class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-600 border-t-0 rounded-b-sm shadow-md p-5 md:p-10"
      >
        <h3 class="heading-2 dark:text-slate-700">
          <a
            href="https://www.newline.co/courses/beginners-guide-to-real-world-react"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            From Aspire To Hired
          </a>
        </h3>
        <div class="prose max-w-none prose-bubblegum dark:text-slate-700">
          <p>
            I've helped people get into coding and land their first job as a
            developer. They did it. I did it. You can do it too!
          </p>
          <p>
            This ebook pulls together a collection of my most popular articles
            including topics on:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Getting into development,</li>
            <li>What to learn as a frontend developer,</li>
            <li>How to look for and land a job in the tech industry,</li>
            <li>...and more</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-center">
            <script src="https://gumroad.com/js/gumroad.js"></script>
            <Button
              href="https://gum.co/WssIGB"
              text="Get the ebook"
              variant="primary"
              external
            />
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="my-8">
      <div class="">
        <a
          href="https://payhip.com/b/eUkN9/af68e8e19714362"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <Image src={techVaImg} alt="Tech VA Blueprint cover" />
        </a>
      </div>
      <div
        class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-600 border-t-0 rounded-b-sm shadow-md p-5 md:p-10"
      >
        <h3 class="heading-2 dark:text-slate-700">
          <a
            href="https://payhip.com/b/eUkN9/af68e8e19714362"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            The Tech VA Blueprint: From Zero Skills to Your First Global Client.
          </a>
        </h3>
        <div class="prose max-w-none prose-bubblegum dark:text-slate-700">
          <p>
            I was hugely honoured to be asked to contribute to this fantastic
            publication created by my good friend and student Joel PJ Mantoss.
          </p>
          <p>
            Joel has put together a comprehensive guide to becoming a successful
            Tech Virtual Assistant, even if you have no prior experience or
            skills.
          </p>
          <p></p>
            This guide covers everything you need to know to get started, including:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>A 5-part guide that takes you from start to finish to help launch your career.</li>
            <li>The "Core Trinity" skillset, three skills that will make you a one-person digital marketing powerhouse.</li>
            <li>Real-World Case Studies.</li>
            <li>Discover additional skills that command higher rates.</li>
            <li>Curated VA job platform list.</li>
            <li>Honest &amp; authentic advice: No fluff, no false promises.</li>
            <li>...and more</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-center">
            <script src="https://gumroad.com/js/gumroad.js"></script>
            <Button
              href="https://payhip.com/b/eUkN9/af68e8e19714362"
              text="Grab your copy"
              variant="primary"
              external
            />
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
